banker trust issu stg/dlr currenc warrant banker trust intern ltd said it is issu 200,000 stg call/dlr put currenc warrant at an initi offer price of 31.25 dlr per warrant . the issu is guarante by banker trust new york corp. each warrant entitl the holder to exchang 500 dlr for stg at a rate of 1.60 stg/dlr and the minimum number of warrant exercis or tradeabl is 100. exercis period for the warrant will run from april 22 , 1987 until march 17 , 1989. payment is due april 15 , 1987 .